title: Stocks to Watch: Has the Bear Market Ended?
description: Barron's senior managing editor Lauren R. Rublin and deputy editor Ben Levisohn discuss the outlook for financial markets, Elon Musk's Twitter deal, the ins and outs of stock splits, and coming corporate earnings.
